snippet.title: ShowBiz Minute: Heard, TIFF, Royals
snippet.description:
Amber Heard says Depp tried to throw her sister down stairs; Spike Lee doc of David Byrne's Broadway show to open TIFF; Royals release photos to mark Prince George's 7th birthday. (July 22)
